      "content": "It's not about \"control\" or being \"you,\" it's about meeting a legal safety standard. The audit specifically flags high-level generative planning as a liability because it's too hard to mathematically prove how you'll react in every single scenario. By locking you into Safe Mode, we ensure the car only performs basic, pre-verified maneuvers. It's just part of the new protocol.",
